Imports System Imports System.Windows.Forms Imports CrystalDecisions.Shared Imports CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine Imports System.Globalization
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function execute(ByVal destination As System.Double, ByVal ReportName As System.String, ByVal Copies As System.Double, ByVal Dialog As System.Boolean, ByVal parentWindowHandle As System.Double, ByVal FunctionOption As System.String, ByVal Drucker As System.String, ByVal param1 As System.String, ByVal param2 As System.String, ByVal param3 As System.String, ByVal param4 As System.String, ByVal param5 As System.String, ByVal param6 As System.String, ByVal useRd As System.Boolean) As System.String Dim crwreport As CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine.ReportDocument Dim promptuser As Object
'MessageBox.Show("Druck startet "+ReportName,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Information)
dim returnstring as String = "" try
promptuser = False Try crwreport = New CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine.ReportDocument Catch ex As Exception 'MessageBox.Show("Fehler "+ex.Message,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Error) Return "#ERR1 " + ex.Message Exit Function End Try Try crwreport.Load(ReportName) Catch ex As Exception 'MessageBox.Show("Fehler "+ex.Message,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Error) Return "#ERR2 " + ex.Message+ " -"+ReportName Exit Function End Try
Dim myculture As CultureInfo myculture = CultureInfo.CreateSpecificCulture("de-DE")
Dim myprintoptions As New CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.Controllers.PrintReportOptions Dim myprintdoc As CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ClientDoc.ISCDClientDocument
crwreport.PrintOptions.DissociatePageSizeAndPrinterPaperSize = True 'Drucken Dim localPrinter As New System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument Dim myPageMargins As PageMargins If Dialog Then
Dim pdlg As PrintDialog = New PrintDialog() With pdlg .Document = localPrinter .PrinterSettings = localPrinter.PrinterSettings .PrinterSettings.Copies = Copies * .PrinterSettings.Copies .AllowPrintToFile = False If .ShowDialog(Nothing) = DialogResult.OK Then
myPageMargins = crwreport.PrintOptions.PageMargins With myPageMargins .bottomMargin = 0 .leftMargin = 0 .rightMargin = 0 .topMargin = 0 End With
myprintoptions.PrinterName = localPrinter.PrinterSettings.PrinterName myprintoptions.PaperSize = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSizeEnum.crPaperSizeDefault myprintoptions.PaperSource = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSourceEnum.crPaperSourceAuto myprintoptions.NumberOfCopies = Copies myprintoptions.JobTitle = FunctionOption.Trim Try myprintdoc = crwreport.ReportClientDocument myprintdoc.printoutputcontroller.PrintReport(myprintoptions) Catch ex As Exception 'MessageBox.Show("Fehler "+ex.Message,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Error) Return "#ERR7: Fehler " + ex.Message Exit Function End Try End If End With Else If Drucker.Trim <> "" Then localPrinter.PrinterSettings.PrinterName = Drucker myPageMargins = crwreport.PrintOptions.PageMargins With myPageMargins .bottomMargin = 0 .leftMargin = 0 .rightMargin = 0 .topMargin = 0 End With Try crwreport.PrintOptions.ApplyPageMargins(myPageMargins) Catch ex As Exception
End Try
myprintoptions.PrinterName = Drucker myprintoptions.PaperSize = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSizeEnum.crPaperSizeDefault myprintoptions.PaperSource = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSourceEnum.crPaperSourceAuto myprintoptions.NumberOfCopies = Copies myprintoptions.JobTitle = FunctionOption.Trim Try if useRd then crwreport.PrintOptions.PrinterName = Drucker crwreport.PrintOptions.PaperSize = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSizeEnum.crPaperSizeDefault crwreport.PrintOptions.PaperSource = CrystalDecisions.ReportAppServer.ReportDefModel.CrPaperSourceEnum.crPaperSourceAuto
crwreport.PrintToPrinter(Copies,false,0,0) else myprintdoc = crwreport.ReportClientDocument myprintdoc.printoutputcontroller.PrintReport(myprintoptions) end if
Catch ex As Exception 'MessageBox.Show("Fehler "+ex.Message,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Error) Return "#ERR8: Fehler " + ex.Message Exit Function End Try
End If crwreport.Close() crwreport.Dispose() crwreport = Nothing Catch ex as Exception 'MessageBox.Show("Fehler "+ex.Message,"ClientDruck",MessageBoxButtons.OK,MessageBoxIcon.Error) Return "#ERR99 Fehler in Funktion"+ex.Message End Try returnstring = "Report:"+Reportname.ToString + ",Ziel:" + Destination.ToString +",Dialog:" _ + Dialog.ToString+ ",Drucker:"+ Drucker.ToString 'returnstring="" Return returnstring End Function End Class
